YOUR TASK:
          For a given N, return an arraylist containing the sum of even and odd integers of the first N natural numbers.

CODE:
     class Solution{
    static ArrayList<Integer> getSum(int N){
        ArrayList<Integer>result=new ArrayList<>();
        int evenSum=0;
        int oddSum=0;
        for(int i=1;i<=N;i++){
            if(i%2==0){
                evenSum+=i;
            }else{
                oddSum+=i;
            }
        }
        result.add(evenSum);
        result.add(oddSum);
        return result;
    }
}

RESULT:
      Input:
      N = 1
      Output:
      0 1
